Class EventForm

  • java.lang.Object
    • forms.ModelForm<Event>
      • forms.EventForm

  • public final class EventForm
extends ModelForm<Event>
    EventForm is responsible for process of events creation. instance field is reference to Event associated with this form (in case its null new object is created).
    Author:
    stnatic

    ModelForm
